{"tid":2154273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿政府施政 廚師掟雜物出馬路判社會服務令120小時 賠償50元閃燈維修費","createTime":"2020-08-13T04:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T05:25:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3533cb56b08ccac5b4bf5f4a0385821678282b66","tid":2154273,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/N4S6CX6LWRAADKVTCW7GDHORJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FN4S6CX6LWRAADKVTCW7GDHORJQ%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=958ddc32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FN4S6CX6LWRAADKVTCW7GDHORJQ%2F&h=288d770a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/N4S6CX6LWRAADKVTCW7GDHORJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n男廚師聲稱對政府施政不滿，去年12月清晨上班途中，將塑膠圍欄及閃燈等雜物拋出馬路堵路，廚師事後被捕，他早前承認公眾地方造成阻礙罪。裁判官今判刑指考慮被告當日作為無造成人命傷亡及財物損失，接納他有悔意，決定判被告履行社會服務令120小時，同時須賠償50元閃燈維修費。"},{"pid":"d3b9f29d93166ca9cd72f5ddfc7a420840968c85","tid":2154273,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedbf4182e43aa36e29ad20471fd6c098789e7e7","tid":2154273,"uid":91259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"呢個官有冇前科？<br />\n呢幾日都好似冇尻判<br />\n正常反好多<br />\n制裁係咪有震懾效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b633a3d1af667f3a1847d48b3c3dc5c6d86e62f","tid":2154273,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cedbf4182e43aa36e29ad20471fd6c098789e7e7","tid":215